thread.title: Bernie Filieo

author: Bernie Filieo
title: Bernie Filieo
text:
Generally, good part availability and delivery service.
Website difficult to locate part wanted even with the part #.
Receipt sent was a two page deal with the company (Easy Keys) heading NOWHERE ON the second page. My company receipt process requires one page with the vendor name, so I had to cut and fit the two pages together to get the receipt to work which delayed me filing my expense report by 3 days. Not very convenient.
BR Filieo
